Internship

Hi, I'm Jess!

I am currently a Tech Consultant based in NYC who works on the Campaign team at Adobe. I majored in Digital Media Design and minored in Fine Arts at the University of Pennsylvania, where I graduated from the School of Engineering in May 2019.



In my free time, I love cartooning, making art, watching stand up, playing with my two cats, and running.

{/*

Peng and Ink

*/}

Inspired by old New Yorker cartoons, I started my own cartoon instagram called Peng and Ink as an outlet to showcase my humor and creativity. It follows a potato-shaped, sassier, and much smaller version of me as I navigate the ups and downs of work, dating, and everything in between. If you love cartoons or just want a laugh, feel free to give me a follow!:)
